    <topic>
        <title>Entering a Guest Room</title>
        <text>&lt;p  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 50px; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);&quot;&gt;The following are the steps to perform before entering a guest room:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p  0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em; text-indent: 50px; line-height: 1.3em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 18.25px;&quot;&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Knock on the door and announce, &amp;ldquo;Housekeeping!&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Open the door and peek inside to make sure that there is no guest.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Position the housekeeping cart in front of the door as if to block it.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Fill in the Room Assignment Sheet with your details:&lt;br  0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot; /&gt;
 &amp;bull; Name&lt;br  0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot; /&gt;
 &amp;bull; Floor of rooms to be cleaned&lt;br  0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot; /&gt;
 &amp;bull; Shift&amp;nbsp;&lt;br  0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot; /&gt;
 &amp;bull; Date&lt;br  0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot; /&gt;
 And place this sheet inside the vanity table drawer&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Check if there is enough light to easily see the room. Open the lights if they are not yet opened.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;session_list&quot;  0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.99em;&quot;&gt;Bring in your cleaning materials. The vacuum should be placed at the far end of the room. The cleaning tools caddy should be placed inside the bathroom.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</text>
